      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic way to get around town? This vehicle has certainly seen a lot of miles and shows significant wear and tear both inside and out, but it's a great opportunity for someone handy or looking for a low-cost entry into vehicle ownership! It\u2019s lived a full life and is ready for its next chapter with a buyer who appreciates a diamond in the very rough.",
